      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;what-is-ai-customer-support&#34;&gt;What is AI Customer Support?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://main.d1jtfhinlastnr.amplifyapp.com/en/glossary/artificial-intelligence/&#34; title=&#34;Technology that enables computers to learn from experience and make decisions like humans do, rather than just following preset instructions.&#34;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&#34;https://main.d1jtfhinlastnr.amplifyapp.com/en/glossary/customer-support/&#34; title=&#34;Customer support is a team and set of tools that help customers solve problems, answer questions, and get the most value from a product or service.&#34;&gt;customer support&lt;/a&gt; is a system that uses &lt;a href=&#34;https://main.d1jtfhinlastnr.amplifyapp.com/en/glossary/artificial-intelligence/&#34; title=&#34;Technology that enables computers to learn from experience and make decisions like humans do, rather than just following preset instructions.&#34;&gt;artificial intelligence&lt;/a&gt; to automatically respond to customer inquiries. Unlike human agents, &lt;a href=&#34;https://main.d1jtfhinlastnr.amplifyapp.com/en/glossary/artificial-intelligence/&#34; title=&#34;Technology that enables computers to learn from experience and make decisions like humans do, rather than just following preset instructions.&#34;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt; can provide support 24/7, 365 days a year. Key features include instant responses and multilingual capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
